        "brief_title": "Hydroxychloroquine Versus Placebo in COVID-19 Patients at Risk for Severe Disease",
        "acronym": "HYCOVID",
        "official_title": "Hydroxychloroquine Versus Placebo in Patients Presenting COVID-19 Infection and at Risk of Secondary Complication: a Prospective, Multicentre, Randomised, Double-blind Study",
        "sponsors": {
